org.apache.ignite.ml.knn.regression

Class KNNRegressionModel<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ignite.ml.knn.classification.KNNClassificationModel<K,V>
      • org.apache.ignite.ml.knn.regression.KNNRegressionModel<K,V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Function<Vector,Double>, Exportable<KNNModelFormat>, IgniteFunction<Vector,Double>, Model<Vector,Double>

    public class KNNRegressionModel<K,V>
extends KNNClassificationModel<K,V>
    This class provides kNN Multiple Linear Regression or Locally [weighted] regression (Simple and Weighted versions).

    This is an instance-based learning method.

    • Local means using nearby points (i.e. a nearest neighbors approach).
    • Weighted means we value points based upon how far away they are.
    • Regression means approximating a function.
